==English==
===Noun===
'''discourse'''

# [[verbal]] [[expression]], either in [[speech]] or [[writing]]
# verbal [[exchange]] or [[conversation]]
# a [[formal]] [[lengthy]] [[exposition]] of some [[subject]], either [[spoken]] or [[written]]
# (in social sciences): an [[institutionalized]] way of [[thinking]], a [[social]] boundary defining what can be said about a specific [[topic]] (term of [[Wikipedia:Michel Foucault|Michel Foucault]])

